.. confval:: USER_DB

   Full path to the IM user DB json file.
   To restrict the users that can access the IM service.
   Comment it or set a blank value to disable user check.
   The default value is empty.
   JSON format of the file::

        {
                "users": [
                        {
                                "username": "user1",
                                "password": "pass1"
                        },
                        {
                                "username": "user2",
                                "password": "pass2"
                        }
                ]
        }

